                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Day 14: Final Reflection</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">A final Socratic Seminar discussing the unit's texts and themes, connecting them to modern society.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

